name: Black Souls hypernetwork for WD 1.4
description:
This is a test hyperrnetwork to see what WD 1.4 (and models based on SD 2.1) is capable of.

This hypernetwork is heavily inspired of Black Souls and was trained on some Sushi Yuusha Toro's artworks (Black Souls's author/artist/dev) and somes Black Souls 2 CGs.
It was trained on the first epoch of Waifu Diffusion 1.4 (Anime) [8cbce067] at 512x512 with a learning rate of 5e-5:149,5e-6:10000,5e-7:20000.

In some cases, adding "sketch" or/and "jaggy lines" to the prompt can improve result.

I recommand to not use WD 1.4's quality modifiers (best quality, normal quality,etc...) with that hypernetwork especially as a negative prompt (worst quality,lowres,etc...)
